  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>This sinuous whip reflects all light off its plated steel surfaces.</em></p><p><strong>1st Level:</strong> You gain a +1 bonus to melee distance with weapon abilities using this weapon. Additionally, any damage-dealing weapon ability using the weapon against a target who has [[potency A average]] also leaves that target [[/apply bleeding save]].</p><p><strong>5th Level:</strong> The weapon’s bonus to melee distance increases to +2. Additionally, any weapon ability that deals rolled damage using the weapon gains a [[/damage 3]]{+3} damage bonus against any target who is bleeding.</p><p><strong>9th Level:</strong> The weapon’s bonus to melee distance increases to +3. Additionally, if you use a signature ability using the weapon that targets one or more bleeding creatures, you can use the same ability again immediately as a maneuver.</p>",
